title: Coated electrodes for liquid thermoelectric conversion devices to enhance Fe2+/Fe3+ redox kinetics
content:
Sustainable Energy Fuels, 2024, Advance Article
DOI: 10.1039/D4SE00220B, Paper
Touya Aiba, Dai Inoue, Yutaka Moritomo
A graphite-dispersion coated electrode enhances the output power of a LTE by 37.5% as compared with that of a LTE composed of a conventional graphite sheet.
